## Dataset Availability Statement

This work utilizes three publicly available benchmark datasets for few-shot learning experiments:

- **CUB-200-2011**: Caltech-UCSD Birds 200-2011 dataset, which contains 200 bird species with a total of 11,788 images.  
  Available at: https://www.vision.caltech.edu/datasets/cub_200_2011/

- **CIFAR-FS**: A few-shot learning version of the CIFAR-100 dataset, derived from the official CIFAR dataset provided by the University of Toronto.  
  Available at: https://www.cs.toronto.edu/~kriz/cifar.html

- **miniImageNet**: A subset of the ImageNet dataset used for few-shot learning, originally introduced by Vinyals et al.  
  Available at: https://github.com/yaoyao-liu/mini-imagenet-tools

These datasets are publicly accessible and used solely for academic research purposes in this study.
